Title: Series: Recueil Basan
Description: A man with a cap (Rembrandt?), bust facing right; second state with reworking; copy after Rembrandt; from an edition of the Recueil published by Henri Louis Basan around 1810 Etching
Curator's comments: This is a copy in reverse after Rembrandt's 'Self-portrait of Rembrandt with Saskia' (New Hollstein 158), with Saskia left out. For the original etching see F,4.22. For comment on the volume, which was published by Henri Louis Basan around 1810, see 1941,0327.11.1
Bibliographic references: New Hollstein (Dutch & Flemish) / The New Hollstein: Dutch and Flemish etchings, engravings and woodcuts 1450-1700 (158) (Rembrandt; copy g.II)
